  Title: The Man of Many Qualities
  By: R. G. H. Siu
  Source:
    ID: ce3f70aa-4448-4cfd-a1b7-4a32eb5e8df0
    Title: I Ching
  Locus:
    Page: 12-13
Hexagram: 1 - ䷀ - Ch'ien
Locus:
  Line: 3
Title: Creativity
---
The man’s fame begins to spread. Such periods of transition are always
unsettling. There is tension in the air. But the man retains his integrity
and avoids being swept along by the masses, which flock to him. He remains
active, vigilant, careful, and apprehensive. The prevention of mistakes
under perilous circumstances is ever on his mind.
